oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Songs From the Heart at the Bluebird Cafe
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: McDonald, Michael, 1952-; Bluebird Café (Restaurant : Nashville, Tenn.); Woodcuts (prints); Musical instruments; Guitar;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (blue, red, and yellow on white) announcing Songs From the Heart announcing the Gary Burr Band, Sarah Hooker, Marilyn Martin, Michael McDonald, Tim Bays, Kim Parent, Charles Victor, and Doug Wayne at the Bluebird Cafe on March 29. Poster features woodcuts of guitars and a heart.
